OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F359A1779970273
OL,3,CWarning issued after increase in so-
OL,4,Ccalled 'doorstep scammers'
OL,6,FA warning has been issued to people
OL,7,Fliving in the south of Scotland after
OL,8,Fan increase in so-called "doorstep
OL,9,Fscammers".
OL,11,FResidents are being told to be
OL,12,Fvigilant as police try to crack down
OL,13,Fon rogue traders.
OL,15,FThe most common doorstep scams in the
OL,16,Flast year have been people offering
OL,17,Froof repairs, gardening work and
OL,18,Fenergy-saving measures.
OL,20,FIt comes as a nationwide campaign
OL,21,F'Shut Out Scammers' has been launched.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/3
