OL,3,CWarning issued after increase in so-
OL,4,Ccalled 'doorstep scammers'
OL,6,FAs people continue to struggle with
OL,7,Fprice increases and rising energy
OL,8,Fbills, reports have been made to
OL,9,FPolice Scotland and Trading Standards
OL,10,Fof rogue traders and companies
OL,11,Fscamming consumers by providing
OL,12,Fmisleading information about products
OL,13,Fand services and posting misleading
OL,14,Freviews online.
OL,16,FSteps to take if you believe a cold
OL,17,Fcaller could be a scammer:
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/3
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
